    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine, showroom-ready shape. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car feel! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
