    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six mastery. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled, the 3.2L powerplant delivers linear torque up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already addressed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and shows zero signs of cathodic degradation or mechanical fatigue. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
