      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, retaining its deep, factory luster without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin feels and smells brand new; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and all tactile surfaces remain crisp and matte. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by certified technicians, with a thick folder of records to prove its pedigree. Every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
