    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total beauty. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape that it practically still has that new-car smell! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows\u2014the exterior is stunning and the interior is completely spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. If you're looking for a ride that's been pampered and kept in top-notch condition, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
